  "detailed_description": "​<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/3c8fc4587c973f4bd8aff1c4663e7d84.poster.avif?t=1550977947\" width=192 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/3c8fc4587c973f4bd8aff1c4663e7d84.webm?t=1550977947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/3c8fc4587c973f4bd8aff1c4663e7d84.mp4?t=1550977947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>UFO Simulator Control Master is a physics based arcade/simulation game.<br><br>The goal of this game is to <span class=\"bb_strike\">abduct</span> rescue missing astronauts by controlling a UFO in space. Get through the narrow passes, dodge the various traps with delicate control. And evacuate astronauts to the goal <span class=\"bb_spoiler\"><span class=\"bb_strike\">Area 51?</span></span> within the time limit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/fa7f0c44ac942181e5383dc19ad72c11.poster.avif?t=1550977947\" width=192 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/fa7f0c44ac942181e5383dc19ad72c11.webm?t=1550977947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/fa7f0c44ac942181e5383dc19ad72c11.mp4?t=1550977947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/6405c9bb73d4a986989deba59be57005.poster.avif?t=1550977947\" width=192 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/6405c9bb73d4a986989deba59be57005.webm?t=1550977947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/6405c9bb73d4a986989deba59be57005.mp4?t=1550977947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can explore the mystery and danger of space.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are two main play modes, including Arcade stages (2.5D style) and Simulation stages (3D style).</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The game uses a check point system so you will not lose your progress.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Realistic UFO flight physics.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Now you can enjoy the game in English, French, and Korean.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/b7b95bdb26ef7a668c9160f3bb974bef.poster.avif?t=1550977947\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/b7b95bdb26ef7a668c9160f3bb974bef.webm?t=1550977947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/b7b95bdb26ef7a668c9160f3bb974bef.mp4?t=1550977947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/273594f691352796db01e94501c85f0d.poster.avif?t=1550977947\" width=192 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/273594f691352796db01e94501c85f0d.webm?t=1550977947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/273594f691352796db01e94501c85f0d.mp4?t=1550977947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>This is Steam Greenlight (Greenlit) game. Thanks for all the supports!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/848070/extras/greenLightUfoSimulator.PNG?t=1550977947\" /></span>",
